CAPE TOWN – Triple murder accused Henri Van Breda has denied attacking or killing any of his family members. The much-awaited testimony of triple murder accused Van Breda saw the public gallery packed to the rafters in the Western Cape High Court. WATCH: Henri van Breda takes the stand in murder trial He’s accused of the axe killings of his mother, Theresa, father, Martin and brother, Rudi, at their luxury home in Stellenbosch in 2015. Just a day before his 23rd birthday, Van Breda gives his version of events. eNCA